title: Janis Joplin - Janis: A Collection of 16 Janis Joplins Classics
description: (Piano/Vocal/Guitar Artist Songbook). A collection of 16 Joplin classics as performed live and on records from 1963-70: Me And Bobby McGee * Piece Of My Heart * Mercedes Benz * Tell Mama * Get It While You Can * many others. Includes b&w photographs.
author: Janis Joplin
